STEDI BA9s Bayonet LED Light Conversion Globe. Often used as parkers, licence plates & interior lighting.

PACKAGED PERFORMANCE.

Coming Soon.

LOW POWER, HIGH BRIGHTNESS. 

Coming Soon.

APPLICATION

Coming Soon.

DETAILS

You’ve upgraded your headlights to LED now your looking at your parkers in all their awful amber glory. Our BA9S LED are the finishing touch to bring the front end of your car back in to the 20th century.

KEY TECHNICAL FEATURES | BA9S

  • CANBUS friendly – Error free operation
  • Not Polarity Sensitive – our BA9S wont fail if you plug them in the wrong way.
  • Constant Current circuit – Avoids compromising LED life & provides consistent illumination across all LEDs
  • Compatible from 9v to 30v circuits.
  • 3SMD LED for uniform light distribution

COMMON USES FOR BA9S GLOBES

  • Interior Dome Lights
  • Dash Lights
  • Gauges
  • License Plate Lights
  • Footwell
  • Courtesy

Sold in packs of 2

SPECIFICATIONS

HOUSING MATERIAL Aluminium
LED 3030
POWER 0.2a @ 13.6v
COMPATIBLE VOLTAGE DC 12v and 24v
LIFESPAN 30,000 Hours
CANBUS Compatible
CONNECTOR TYPE BA9S
INGRESS PROTECTION IP65
OPERATING TEMP -40°c to + 80°c
CERTIFICATION CE, ROHS

 

 

 

WHAT’S IN THE BOX

  • 2 x STEDI BA9S LED Lights
  • User Instruction Manual
